# Exclude the entire parent monorepo — prevents invalid relative paths in the VSIX.
# vsce uses minimatch; `**` alone does not match `../` or `../../` prefixes,
# so each traversal depth needs its own explicit pattern.
../../**
../**

# Exclude everything inside this package, then re-allow only what the extension needs.
**
!dist/**
!icons/**
!language-configuration.json
!language-server/dist/**
!snippets/**
!syntaxes/**
!package.json
!README.md
!CHANGELOG.md
